e useful for the design of systems on platforms including valve-based and droplet-based platforms. In a separate publication by Shen et al. (J. Am. Chem. Soc., 2011, {DOI}: 10.1021/ja2060116), this approach is used to design and test digital {RT}-{PCR} devices for quantifying {RNA}.},
